{"word":"ἀπόφασις","slug":"ἀπόφασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπόφασις1</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀπόφημι'><el>ἀπόφημι</el></a>\n<p/><i>a denial, negation</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>κατάφασις</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>ἀπόφασις2</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποφαίνω'><el>ἀποφαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a sentence, decision</i> of a court, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a list, inventory</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}